file structure:
def.h   		---------- common header
node.h  		---------- definition of syntax tree
tree.h  		---------- implementation of syntax tree
small.l 		---------- lexical analyzer
small.y         	---------- syntax analyzer
semantics.h     	---------- check semantic errors
intermediate.h  	---------- intermediate code generation
optimize.h      	---------- optimizations
codegen.h      		---------- MIPS code generation
test                    ---------- simple test case
InterCode               ---------- intermediate code for the simple test case provided
MIPSCode.s              ---------- MIPS code for the simple test case provided
scc                     ---------- executable file
README                  ---------- this file
makefile                ---------- makefile
5142029014-report.pdf   ---------- project report


how to use:
run ./scc testfile in the terminal, you will get IR code in InterCode and MIPS code in MIPSCode.s
or run ./scc input output in the terminal, you will get IR code in InterCode and MIPS code in output

